		title: "The LV Hull"
		icon: {id: "gtceu:lv_machine_hull", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Low Voltage Machine Hull is GregTech's base building block. Every LV machine is built from one. It now requires Manasteel — the gate you built in Chapter 6 is intentional.", "You are not a factory worker yet. You are a mage who decided to go industrial. The Hull reflects that."]
		tasks: [{
