		title: "Medium Voltage"
		icon: {id: "gtceu:mv_machine_hull", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The MV Machine Hull. Aluminium plates from the EBF, an Epic M&S stone as the core — combat progression feeds into industrial progression. Eight plates, one stone. Craft it.", "MV machines run faster, process more operations per second, and handle recipe chains that LV machines can't touch. This is where GregTech stops being early game."]
